author: Huawei
description:
Madrid set the stage for cloud innovation at HUAWEI CONNECT EUROPE 2025. From demos to discussions, one message stood out: #HuaweiCloud is evolving to harness AI at scale, and the #Huawei partner ecosystem is thriving as a result. 
 
Discover how Huawei partners are positioning their enterprises to stay ahead by integrating advanced cloud capabilities into their services. Watch the highlights from #HUAWEICONNECT to explore insights and the latest trends driving digital transformation across Europe: https://bit.ly/4qI51Op
title: Huawei Partner Ecosystem is Thriving at HUAWEI CONNECT

author: Huawei
description:
#Huawei Cloud is empowering leading European companies with enhanced AI-driven cloud innovations. Ronald van Loon explored the latest multi-cloud engine and other innovative solutions at the #HuaweiCloud showcase at #HUAWEICONNECT EUROPE 2025.
 
Learn the latest insights from Europe's largest digital advertising group, Azerion; Spain's second-largest hotel chain, Barceló; and Swiss infrastructure inspection company, Screening Eagle. Watch the highlights to see what’s driving digital transformation in Europe: https://bit.ly/47sPAlz
title: European Companies Embrace an AI-Ready Cloud at HUAWEI CONNECT
